Class Subscribed

java.lang.Object
dryclean.cyprusDryCleanEntities.User
dryclean.cyprusDryCleanEntities.Customer
dryclean.cyprusDryCleanEntities.Subscribed
All Implemented Interfaces:
customerManagement, Comparable<Customer>
public class Subscribed extends Customer
Represents a subscribed customer in the system. Subscribed customers receive a 10% discount on all orders and are required to pay a deposit. Extends the Customer class.
Version:
23.0
Author:
Ferhat Kasim Koc
